Package: AOUSDOHtools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Analyzing AOU SDOH Survey Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Zhirui",
                  family = "Deng",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "zhd52@pitt.edu")
Description: A collection of functions designed for processing and analyzing 
    survey data from the All of Us Social Determinants of Health (AOUSDOH) 
    program. The package provides tools for calculating various health and 
    well-being scores such as neighborhood cohesion, social support, perceived 
    discrimination, perceived stress, and other survey-based metrics. It 
    simplifies common tasks in survey data analysis, including recoding, score 
    calculation, and variable creation.
